[Results of entomological investigations related to SBV have, so far, come also from Belgium and Italy. Data from other countries will be welcomed. It may be anticipated that vector studies will be enhanced within the EU-planned research into SBV.

It may be assumed that SBV will be one of the subjects reviewed and discussed during this week's 80th General Session of the OIE in Paris. SBV is not (yet) included in OIE's list. So far, it has been reported by the affected member-countries as an "emerging disease." - Mod.AS

